data.Name: The Kinky Fingers
data.Bio: The Kinky Fingers pull from the vaults and traditions of American music coast to coast, Canada to Mexico; blending elements of 50s and 60s rock, western swing, surf music, blues, jazz, and folk. They are an American band in the 21st century. Singer-songwritter / multi-instrumentalist Tayler Doyle started The Kinky Fingers in the summer or 2012 as a collective and has incorporated numerous musicians and arrangements for the group.
